@BookPromoTracker_HostAddress = http://localhost:5195
@bookId = 3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
@alertId = 7ba85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6

### Listar livros cadastrados
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar livro por ID
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Cadastrar livro com URL da Amazon Brasil
POST {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "O Iluminado",
  "author": "Stephen King",
  "productUrl": "https://www.amazon.com.br/dp/8532520709",
  "targetPrice": 35.00
}

###

### Atualizar livro
PUT {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "O Iluminado",
  "author": "Stephen King",
  "productUrl": "https://www.amazon.com.br/Livro/dp/8532520709?ref_=abc",
  "targetPrice": 30.00,
  "isActive": true
}

###

### Ativar monitoramento
PATCH {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/activate
Accept: application/json

###

### Desativar monitoramento
PATCH {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/deactivate
Accept: application/json

###

### Remover livro
DELETE {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}

###

### Registrar preço manual
POST {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/prices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 29.90,
  "currency": "BRL",
  "observedAt": "2026-07-13T23:15:00Z"
}

###

### Listar histórico de preços
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/price-history
Accept: application/json

###

### Buscar menor preço registrado
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/lowest-price
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar alertas
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/alerts
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar alertas não lidos
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/alerts?unreadOnly=true
Accept: application/json

###

### Consultar quantidade de alertas não lidos
GET {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/alerts/unread-count
Accept: application/json

###

### Marcar alerta como lido
PATCH {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/read

###

### Marcar alerta como não lido
PATCH {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/alerts/{{alertId}}/unread

###

### Endpoint descontinuado — verificação automática de preço
POST {{BookPromoTracker_HostAddress}}/api/books/{{bookId}}/check-price
Accept: application/json

###
